                                                Chinese Energy Holdings Ltd
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Chinese Energy Holdings Ltd operates within the Electronic parts and equipment sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Chinese Energy Holdings Ltd with three other
	
			companies in this sector in Hong Kong:
		
	Mobicon Group Limited
	
		(2017
	sales of 627.77 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$80.38  million]
		),
	
	HKC International Holdings Limited
	
		(170.69 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$21.85  million]
		), and
	
	Gold Tat Group International Ltd
	
		(567.41 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$72.65  million]
		).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	
		During the year ended March of 2017, sales at
		Chinese Energy Holdings Ltd were HK$537.43 million (US$68.81 million).
	
		This
		
			is
		
				an
			
			increase of 29.1%
		
		 versus 2016, when the company's sales were HK$416.35 million.
	

	





 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










